,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:59:38.000Z","msg":"6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffdea7a260941e7b3c61fc1db1b22af9670a793","tid":134473,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f47d1f8b41f584474011cade817012dcc5e5029","tid":134473,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f372cee5a590aa1e3904db23039f728c91711af4","tid":134473,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"絲打?<br />\n俾我屌返獲就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049c1c97acdd9e39205da4e9b7d59afaca4cc8e6","tid":134473,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c99448aaae1bede82e27db26d748143d7998c8","tid":134473,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T22:25:48.000Z","msg":"其實我既日常生活真係俾呢件事影響得好嚴重<br />\n每晚都訓唔到 導致第日都過唔到正常生活<br />\n除左放縱自己既玩樂 其他所有正經事都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n琴晚崩潰左 一個人凌晨兩三點係條街到喊左出黎<br />\n趁住個刻既勇氣 打左俾佢 想問清楚究竟點解要俾假希望我<br />\n結果當然冇人聽電話 喊住錄左個留言俾佢<br />\n<br />\n然後 無謂既自卑心又發作<br />\n個留言既內容淨係喊聲<br />\n同埋 同佢道歉 話以後唔會再騷擾佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後 第日收到就係佢話佢訓左既voice message <br />\n本來想唔覆 但愈諗愈唔忿氣<br />\n數番 隔左廿四個鐘 終於覆左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfcca3871ff1a26e6f4674c36367e388375f320","tid":134473,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T22:29:14.000Z","msg":"佢都唔鍾意你<br />\n佢只係當睇緊人舞獅<br />\n同班朋友一齊笑下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79395717d526b0b6fdd16ec65cbb44d5e49ea395","tid":134473,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T22:30:34.000Z","msg":"利申 對感情好認真 甚至係執著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩中意同愛 <br />\n甚至好少會真正對一個異性有興趣<br />\n因為見識過太多糟糕既異性<br />\n或者係從頭到尾都唔識去相信人"},{"pid":"d2dc1485e3981410dc31cf6b3c8cb45e3d0cda3f","tid":134473,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T22:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢都唔鍾意你<br />\n佢只係當睇緊人舞獅<br />\n同班朋友一齊笑下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 道歉吖我要佢既道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fef9ca10f1acec33b1991e4ef88c8f735eddb8","tid":134473,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T23:00:55.000Z","msg":"三個月姐<br />\n人地唔撚鍾意你咪算囉<br />\n何必搞到自己咁樣衰<br />\n今日你會接受佢<br />\n第日都會搵到個代替佢既人"},{"pid":"03542ca79bd0ebcfe3c6f969cd97085b4e9dccb1","tid":134473,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T23:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個月姐<br />\n人地唔撚鍾意你咪算囉<br />\n何必搞到自己咁樣衰<br />\n今日你會接受佢<br />\n第日都會搵到個代替佢既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次呢個我等左兩年先遇到<br />\n兩年前有個都幾中意 <br />\n不過俾朋友捷足先登玩完三個月飛埋<br />\n基於朋友既立場 事後中意還中意 我都冇點理個個對象<br />\n到兩年後呢個............."},{"pid":"9329d11614995d00e31c4e01579b459dcfa84d2a","tid":134473,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T23:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三個月姐<br />\n人地唔撚鍾意你咪算囉<br />\n何必搞到自己咁樣衰<br />\n今日你會接受佢<br />\n第日都會搵到個代替佢既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次呢個我等左兩年先遇到<br />\n兩年前有個都幾中意 <br />\n不過俾朋友捷足先登玩完三個月飛埋<br />\n基於朋友既立場 事後中意還中意 我都冇點理個個對象<br />\n到兩年後呢個.............</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要求太高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩年又點姐<br />\n你以為自己係到頹 人地就會鍾意返你咩"},{"pid":"896063